<Theme id="default" displayName="default" version="2">
    <!--
        Theme rules:
        1. Only shared component categories are supported. Theme values must
           describe a reusable UI category, not a specific page, window, or
           control instance.
        2. Do not add page/control names such as settings.searchInput,
           linkEdit.nameField, searchDialog.keywordEdit, or any similar
           per-screen override. Unsupported components are ignored by the
           loader.
        3. Customize common controls through the shared categories below:
           text, label, panel, field, edit, button, primaryButton, iconButton, miniButton, checkbox,
           toggle, radio, comboBox, tabButton, list, listItem, scrollbar,
           slider, dialog, menuItem, linkItem, majorNavItem, minorNavItem,
           titleButton, tooltip, separator, etc.
        4. New themeable UI must first be mapped to an existing shared category.
           Add a new category only when it represents a reusable component type
           across screens.
